    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels for Medium model risk (modelRiskLevel 3). The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) reflects the single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol and is accepted given the quasi-static, room-temperature nature of the COU and the conservative character of the F1717 loading scenario. Quantitative output comparison (E/uval < 1.96 for all QoIs; percent differences < 10%) provides direct evidence of model adequacy. The assessment team accepts the credibility evidence as sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
